jp.go.aist.six.oval.core.interpreter

Class OvaldiProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.aist.six.oval.core.interpreter.OvaldiProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OvalInterpreter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NetworkingOvaldiProxy

    public class OvaldiProxy
extends Object
implements OvalInterpreter
    An ovaldi proxy. The ovaldi is a Mitre's reference implementation which evaluates OVAL Definitions. Based on a set of OVAL Definitions the interpreter collects system information, evaluates it, and generates a detailed OVAL Results file.
